{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_01_01",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃 1話 焦りは禁物",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_coast",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――時は遡り",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Turning back the clock…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月ストとサニピが同時デビューを果たした直後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Right after Moon Tempest and\nSunny Peace make their joint debut",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（早朝。なんとなく目が覚めてしまった俺は）\n（散歩がてら、海岸通りへと足を運んだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Morning. I’m not sure why‚ but I wake up early）\n（and head out to take a walk on the beach.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.966666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…{user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 12.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃？\nおはよう、ずいぶんと早起きなんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono?\nMorning. You’re up early.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます。早朝ランニングは日課なので\nもしかして……知らなかったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning. I always take a morning run.\nWait… you didn’t know that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.466666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "担当アイドルの行動が把握出来ていないなんて\nマネージャー失格じゃないんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re not much of a manager if don’t know\nthe daily routine of your idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……すまない。これじゃあ\n琴乃に頼ってもらえないのも無理はないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sorry. I’m not surprised\nyou don’t trust me like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "分かってるなら、次から気を付けて下さい\nあなたは私の……マネージャーなんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just don’t make the same mistake again.\nYou’re my… manager‚ after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "では、そろそろ行きます\nまだ走り足りないので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I need to keep running.\nI’m not done yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "なら、俺も付き合うよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let me join you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "え……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "レッスンメニューを把握したいし\nもっとみんなとの交流を深めていきたいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to understand your training schedule\nand get to know all of you better.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "……別にいいですけど。知りませんよ？\nどうなっても",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Whatever. Just don’t blame me\nwhen your muscles are screaming tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "私はペースを緩めません\nもし遅れるようなら置いていきます。それで良ければ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not slowing down.\nIf you fall behind‚ I’m leaving you in the dust. Okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――十分後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—10 minutes later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "意外でした\nてっきりすぐに脱落するものだと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was unexpected.\nI thought I’d lose you right away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "はあ、はあ……こ、これくらいは余裕だよ\n馬鹿にされちゃ困るな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*huff* *huff* Th-that was nothing.\nDon’t underestimate me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですか\nなら、もう少しペースを上げさせてもらいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see.\nIn that case‚ let’s speed things up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――十五分後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—15 minutes later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "ふうっ……どうしました？\nペースが乱れ始めていますよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew… What’s the matter?\nYou’re starting to slip behind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――二十分後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—20 minutes later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "も、もうダメだ……\nこれ以上は、さすがに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I’m done…\nI can’t keep going…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2299.9999999999973,
          "startTime": 103.73333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…{user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "お、置いていくんじゃ、なかったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… I thought you were gonna leave me behind?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "そのつもりでしたけど、気が変わりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was planning to‚ but I changed my mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "汗、拭いて下さい\n風邪でも引かれたら困ります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here‚ wipe your sweat with this.\nI don’t want you catching a cold.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ありがとう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-thank you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "お礼はいりません\n倒れられたら、私の活動に影響が出るので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No need to thank me.\nIf you collapse‚ you’ll put a dent in my career.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "……なんですか？　その顔は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes? What’s that look for?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "本当にそれだけですから！\n勘違いしないで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s really all this is!\nDon’t get the wrong idea.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、分かったよ。それにしても\n琴乃は毎日こんな距離を走っているのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ okay. Whatever you say.\nDo you run this far every day?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_01-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。アイドルには体力も必要ですし\nそれに、肺活量は歌唱力にも影響しますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. An idol needs physical stamina.\nLung capacity helps with singing too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
